{"tid":2012193,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚爆不雅片】疑似女網紅闖宜家大尺度拍攝 宜家中國急報警","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T00:44:14.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8dce0c9fbc38dc38f8bd4d9b53a101f31379df0e","tid":2012193,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200510/TTZH2P7MAYKAUTAQJKNGO4SI6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200510%2FTTZH2P7MAYKAUTAQJKNGO4SI6U%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=59a07200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200510%2FTTZH2P7MAYKAUTAQJKNGO4SI6U%2F&h=06d7501b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200510/TTZH2P7MAYKAUTAQJKNGO4SI6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日一段疑似在內地宜家家居（IKEA）拍攝的不雅短片，在網上瘋傳，引發爭議。IKEA中國9日發聲明表示譴責有關行為，並已即時報警。事件並驚動官媒，《環球時報》今日發文批評，宜家官方及警方至今未具體回應事。有傳事發宜家位於廣東廣州，另有網民指，該片疑為經常在公眾地方拍攝尺度極大不雅片的女網紅Fullfive，帶着攝影師到宜家拍攝的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BM5Xi6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBM5Xi6x.jpg&h=4e5317e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c28fbf45d8d9e826b6e97d5425512e2c183583b5","tid":2012193,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"連登=孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f568c612b79e78b3e07153b154b8d0a5851fabb","tid":2012193,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<